blackbox.php<pre><code>&lt;?php
declare(strict_types = 1);

require 'path/to/vendor/autoload.php';

use Innmind\BlackBox\Application;

Application::new([]) #(1)
    -&gt;tryToProve(static function(): \Generator {
        // tests and proofs go here
    })
    -&gt;exit();
</code></pre> <ol> <li>You'll learn in a later chapter what this array is. For now leave it like this.</li> </ol> <p>The function passed to <code>tryToProve</code> must return a <code>Generator</code>. We'll see in the next chapters how to describe tests and proofs.</p> <p>To execute your suite, run <code>php blackbox.php</code> in your terminal.</p>
